## Reports
Framework       | Description
----------------| -----------
[LicenseFinder] | List out gem licenses `bundle exec license_finder report --format html > tmp/reports/licenses.html`.
[RailsERD]      | ERD will be generated in `erd.pdf` after you run `rails db:migrate` but you can also run manually with `bundle exec erd`
[SimpleCov]     | RSpec coverage reports are saved to `tmp/reports/coverage/` and will update when you run `rspec spec`
[Brakeman]      | Check for security vulnerabilities. Run `brakeman`. Report will be saved to `tmp/reports/brakeman.html`.
[Yard]          | See documentation by running `yard server`.
[Inch]          | See documentation analytics by running `inch`.

